images.title: Waves for wheels
images.caption: Venice Skatepark, Los Angeles, California
images.desc: Welcome to the concrete waves of Venice Beach, California, a skateboarder's paradise. Built next to the beach town's sun-kissed shores, Venice Skatepark stands as a testament to the history of skateboarding in the state.
